vvah-sast
=========

This product is an original reimplementation of a 9-stage agentic SAST
pipeline. It does NOT import, call, or bundle any code from the `vvaharness`
package.

Prompt content (stage system prompts, shared triage fragments, specialist and
language lenses, and threat-model baselines) was ported as TEXT CONTENT from
the `vvaharness` project (Visa, Inc. / Project Glasswing), which is licensed
under the Apache License, Version 2.0.

Per Apache-2.0, all ported prompt files retain the upstream license header and
a source pointer; the per-item provenance is recorded in
`prompt-provenance.md`. Porting is content-only and does not constitute a
runtime dependency on `vvaharness`.

